### Tenant A — ürün ekle
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-a

{
  "name": "Tenant A Laptop",
  "price": 999.99
}

### Tenant B — ürün ekle
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-b

{
  "name": "Tenant B Mouse",
  "price": 29.99
}

### Tenant A — sadece kendi ürünlerini görür
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-a

### Tenant B — sadece kendi ürünlerini görür
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-b